"                .body(is(\"userOidc:viewer:user@gmail.com:subject:issuer\"));\n"
"    }\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/security-openid-connect.adoc:994
#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/security-openid-connect.adoc:1066
